Desc: She seeks her revelation subconsciously, but both the stars and the "Sage" are hiding behind the clouds, refusing to answer.

Name: Meet Again
Desc: —"You... remember my name?"—"Of course! You're Nanami's friend, Haicma!"

Name: Dying on the Snowfield
Desc: Right before his mind melts into the snowfield and turns blank... He has a dream.

Name: Missing Out
Desc: Was the person you remember seeing... someone that everyone else had to try to be careful around?

Name: A Sinner's Memory 1
Desc: He's killed his mentor, and no amount of regret can undo what's happened. The only thing he can feel now is the throbs coming from his heart that remind him of what he's done.

Name: A Sinner's Memory 2
Desc: Why...? Captain...

Name: Choice of the Death Fire
Desc: If life is a fire that will eventually lead to death, the boy will definitely choose to burn out than freeze out.

Name: "Monster" in the Box
Desc: I suppose there's nothing wrong with calling you a "monster" when you're the Construct the Ascendants are "feeding" in a jail cell.

Name: Please Aim
Desc: If that was your last warning, then I ask of you... don't miss next time.

Name: Warm Spring
Desc: Only a few pieces of fabric linger on its branches, rattling in the wind inside the quiet orchard. The patterns on them look similar to Field's scarf.

Name: Goodbye
Desc: This time, "goodbye" isn't just a farewell. It is proof that all of you were once by my side.

Name: The Final Choice
Desc: Hope is not an illusion. It's what came out of our countless sacrifices and sufferings!

Name: To the Future
Desc: Noan. My name is Noan. Nice to meet you, Commandant.

Name: Egret's Scars
Desc: A pair of scarred wings, as if a bond that is marked with burning brands.

Name: Cracking Bond
Desc: Falling to the ground, the photo frame has broken with a shrill crack, just as something in their hearts has also shattered.

Name: Home
Desc: From now on, this is Bambinata's home... Mother, Father... and Nessa.

Name: Listen to "Mother"
Desc: Good children, become, family. Doris.

Name: Figure in the Mirror
Desc: Is that the expression when one likes something? The one in the mirror is... her "self"?

Name: A Night of Silent Conversation
Desc: The two are snuggled up together. No more words are needed between them.

Name: A Dream of a Puppet
Desc: Bambinata had a very, very long dream, Mistress.

Name: Another Home
Desc: She cannot remember how she got here, only how she left.

Name: A Home Far Away
Desc: Amidst the dense fog and heavy clouds, rays of dawn shall shine upon Kowloong.

Name: Mark of Time
Desc: It's been so many years, but you haven't changed one bit.

Name: Here or There
Desc: Have "you" been dancing here all the time?

Name: Gate Keeper
Desc: The Gate Keeper falls silent. He stands there quietly, awaiting the challenge of those who attempt to pass.

Name: Journey's End
Desc: Their <THEIR> journey has come to an end.

Name: Falling Leaf
Desc: From thousands of leaves, a red maple leaf falls into her palm.

Name: Floating Dreams
Desc: Time had long forgotten us, but a fresh start awaits you, as well as Kowloong.

Name: Dream's End
Desc: That is a trip they must take before the fresh start.

Name: Mad Dog
Desc: Answer my question!

Name: New Oakley
Desc: You are not welcome here.

Name: Buddy Up
Desc: Let's dance!

Name: The Prey & Inquisition
Desc: I never let my prey run away.

Name: Ashes to Ashes, Dust to Dust
Desc: This punch will put an end to all the past grudges.

Name: Uninvited Guest
Desc: An uninvited guest comes to the tavern later.

Name: Cerberuses Assemble
Desc: Cerberus will decide what Cerberus does!

Name: Radiance
Desc: The setting sun shines upon the roaring engine.

Name: Lingering Smoke
Desc: Trojan! What are you doing?!

Name: Evaluation
Desc: She has never regretted any of the choices she made.

Name: Weight of Life
Desc: Once again, she lifts the weight of life like she has done countless times before.

Name: The Cage 1
Desc: You have walked into a trap.

Name: The Cage 2
Desc: I can see you.

Name: After Story
Desc: The ending may not be perfect.

Name: Beacon
Desc: She embraces the light with her arms.

Name: Into the City
Desc: A silver skyscraper stands there. It used to be the eye through which Earth looks up at the stars.

Name: Comrades
Desc: She plucks the strings. The music travels into the distance.

Name: Twinkling Stars
Desc: She gazes into the distance... into the heaven they long for.

Name: Resolve
Desc: She stares at the figure hidden in the darkness through the mist.

Name: Breaking the Cocoon
Desc: The hairpin is my blade!

Name: Into the Abyss
Desc: What lies at the end of the path should not be hell.

Name: So-Called Heaven
Desc: We'll always find the path to that future. Right?

Name: Solitude
Desc: The grilles were the iron windows of childhood.

Name: Fireworks
Desc: Though its radiance is fleeting, it signifies a small defiance of ours.

Name: Shattered Mirror
Desc: Which window reflects reality?

Name: Deep Dive
Desc: The fading memory is tenacious like the deep sea.

Name: Truth
Desc: Piercing through the shadows, chasing after the secret of the past.

Name: Assassination
Desc: A never-waking dream. Goodbye.

Name: Wound
Desc: To seal the past is to commemorate the future.

Name: Coffin
Desc: A little piece of me dies with every goodbye.

Name: Amber
Desc: An object of sedimentation symbolizes both the start and end.

Name: Swaddle
Desc: A soft yet firm curve, cradling the past of all.

Name: Hibernation
Desc: The barren land transforms into fertile fields, flowers bloom from their slumber.

Name: Salvation
Desc: That war is one I have already fought.

Name: Clarity
Desc: Fantasies are always so perfect, aren't they?

Name: Farewell
Desc: A shard pierces through the air, signifying the end of the story.

Name: Blessing
Desc: Don't worry, just leave it to me.

Name: Time
Desc: I have come a long way since then.

Name: Future
Desc: The people whom I trust and wish to protect are all here.

Name: Return
Desc: A stripped-bare death, a stripped-bare freedom.

Name: Return
Desc: A life that goes on, yet remains lost.

Name: Vibrant Splendors
Desc: Everything remains as beautiful as ever.

Name: Letting Go
Desc: To be reborn, one must first truly die.

Name: From Ruin to Rebirth
Desc: "You're almost there, give it your all!"

Name: Mission Goal
Desc: The gun stays out of harm's way.

Name: Reencounter
Desc: Meeting again, only to part ways once more.

Name: Gift for the Tailor
Desc: You went through all that trouble collecting such fine tools.

Name: Bloody Enlightenment
Desc: The pain spreads through the body like ink dripping into blood vessels.

Name: Splendid Night
Desc: Here, the game is the one true law.

Name: Meridian of Revelation
Desc: There is silver reflection of the ship in the purple grey pupils.

Name: Doomsday Evening
Desc: The revelers will eventually fall into the swamp of revelry one by one.

Name: Pain With Me
Desc: Her lips curl into a smile that hurts her old companion's heart.

Name: Emotional Knot
Desc: Emotions are not allowed in any mission.

Name: Casual Walk
Desc: The fragments cut across the bionic skin, letting out crimson threads into the rain.

Name: Abyss of Bliss
Desc: Your wish will come true as long as you are willing to sacrifice everything.

Name: A Gift From Dusk
Desc: My name is Jetavie. Our meeting here is not by chance.

Name: Countdown
Desc: Everything here, no matter how stable it may appear on the surface... is actually a fragile existence.

Name: bang！
Desc: Accompanied by a thunderous roar that reverberates through the eardrums, magnificent light tears through the thick gunsmoke.

Name: Her "Rebirth"
Desc: When those eyes open one day, what kind of thoughts will it have?

Name: Frozen Night
Desc: The night freezes just before dawn.

Name: Miraculous Reunion
Desc: Her time begins to flow once more.

Name: Collapsed Wonderland
Desc: Wandering in the heart of a destroyed world... How many times has it been now?

Name: Chosen One?
Desc: Let's escape together.

Name: Dawning Luminescence
Desc: They have finally witnessed the real "Daybreak."

Name: Rolling Snow
Desc: Your sharpness, too, will inevitably be dulled until you reach the tragic end that awaits you.

Name: Sea Hunter 1
Desc: Little darling, you're nothing but a damned Hetero-Creature.

Name: Surprise Troop
Desc: A burst of colorful smoke suddenly rises, and before anyone can react, the bombardment begins.

Name: Arm Yourself
Desc: A hero needs a sharp blade, so they lift their swords before them.

Name: Imitation 1
Desc: The bullet tears through the air thick with Punishing energy and the stench of blood, hurtling toward the source of the tense.

Name: Imitation 2
Desc: The sluggish flow of time ends here as, in an instant, the tables are turned.

Name: Blade Dance
Desc: The fire is here.

Name: Sea Hunter 2
Desc: A delicate face, contorted with rage, presses close against its eyes.

Name: Champion
Desc: Use me completely, burn me thoroughly, and be sure to turn these small sparks into a raging wildfire.

Name: Bite 1
Desc: You bite me, and I'll break your teeth. This is how you treat a bad dog.

Name: Bite 2
Desc: Do I... have to say "sorry"... before you'll get up?

Name: Bite 3
Desc: You remember now... do you remember everything?

Name: Bite 4
Desc: ...Great.

Name: Resentment 1
Desc: She knows that person has already reached their destination and will be rewarded with a brilliant future.

Name: Resentment 2
Desc: Our paths will cross again, in a better place.

Name: Innocent Slaughter
Desc: Tap-tap, tap-tap. Light, cheerful steps; a joyous dance.

Name: Dead End
Desc: While life's breath lingers.

Name: Dramatic Murder
Desc: Who is the victim?

Name: Dramatic Murder 2
Desc: I am part of the system, and so are you.

Name: Dramatic Murder 3
Desc: Spider webs become cocoons.

Name: Grand Debut
Desc: Her lance is sharp, like her fighting will—never dulled.

Name: In the Shadows
Desc: An introduction not so pleasant.

Name: Watching Birds Soar
Desc: The stars shine brilliantly tonight.

Name: No One Escapes
Desc: "Prisoners" confined here have no chance of escape.

Name: Silent Barrier
Desc: Lies are barriers, lies are hell.

Name: No Turning Back 1
Desc: These delicate crystals will never melt.

Name: No Turning Back 2
Desc: A gentle breeze stirs as the sun crests the horizon once more.

Name: "Good Night"
Desc: Good night instead of goodbye.

Name: The Image in Memory 1
Desc: "The sun's going down. You should get going."

Name: The Image in Memory 2
Desc: The illusions within dreams will ultimately shatter.

Name: The Image in Memory 3
Desc: She melds into the last golden rays of the setting sun with her wings spread.

Name: On the Brink of Abyss
Desc: Holding a katana in hand, she stands on the brink of an abyss.

Name: Path of Remembrance
Desc: He travelled a long journey before becoming a "Forsaken".

Name: Come Play!
Desc: Games are always more fun with friends, right?

Name: Heart Compass
Desc: She will continue to sail on the course she started.

Name: Candle Light Torment
Desc: The dead are the wax, the living are the wicks. The survivors will carry their light onward, but are also burned by their memories forever.

Name: Land of Bliss
Desc: The pure land has long been destroyed by the Punishing Virus.

Name: Crimson Contract
Desc: This is the ending you've chosen, the contract you've signed with me. We'll journey forever in this world you've envisioned.

Name: The End of the World
Desc: You... and "all of you," have created a fascinating story.

Name: Beyond
Desc: You gaze at the distant lights beyond, hoping to arrive there the next time.

Name: Jetavie
Desc: The light that parts the sea of emptiness will reach another shore. Listen carefully, echo.

Name: Rabbit Hole
Desc: Sweet fruits do not lead to the real Eden. Hope is a fantasy that leeches onto reality.

Name: Night Watcher
Desc: She patrols at night before dawn and indulges herself in the carefree wonderland.

Name: Dawnbreaker
Desc: Through the night and the shadow, a new world will be born, and the song of tomorrow will be played.

Name: Edge of the Blade
Desc: The axe cuts down the bitter winter.

Name: The Light of Dawn
Desc: It's hope that pierces the sky, bathed in the light of day.

Name: Reencounter
Desc: See you never.

Name: Afternoon
Desc: Sunset glow streams through the window, enveloping the entire world in a peaceful, luminous halo.

Name: The Contemplative Gaze of Complex Snow Dreams
Desc: The expression that has appeared countless times in your mind is so gentle... yet so distant.

Name: Nirvatia
Desc: Like a pure and flawless night, like a gentle and earnest sweet rain, it quietly approaches this land, softly unfolding before my eyes.

Name: Midnight Century
Desc: "And now, the savior cuts through chaos, leading us to raise the banner of rebellion—"

Name: The Godfall Revelation
Desc: The four paths of Apocalypse form a Blood Covenant with the savior—together they sever the Collar of the mortal world, letting the corrupt universe be reborn through Judgment in Phoenix Flame.

Name: Terminal
Desc: This journey is wrapping up, so please, all passengers— be good people in your next life, okay?

Name: Plains Dash
Desc: The war has begun— the war to end all wars.

Name: Life and Death Scorched in Ruins
Desc: In this struggle, death triumphs.

Name: Cradlesong and Requiem
Desc: The Supreme Heaven declares that life is the world's ultimate disease. Then he becomes the physician who grants liberation to all living beings.

Name: Volatile Priestess
Desc: The crimson revenant chases flame; the burning flower blazes radiance.
